title: James Comey, one of Trump’s most frequent targets, indicted by prosector installed by president – live

title: White low-income pupils ‘report lowest enthusiasm for school’ in England
summary: Research indicates that boys and girls entering secondary school exhibit the lowest levels of engagement compared to other age groups. This trend raises concerns about their enthusiasm for learning and participation in school activities. Strategies may need to be implemented to boost engagement among these students.

title: Clarkston review – Heartstopper’s Joe Locke joins lonely souls looking to make life matter
summary: Samuel D. Hunter's bleak three-hander features Ruaridh Mollica and Sophie Melville, delivering a powerful narrative. The play is characterized by its subtle yet impactful storytelling. title: Fighter jets purchase would put UK in breach of nuclear treaty, says CND
summary: A legal opinion obtained by a campaign group argues that a recent deal signifies a reversal of the UK's commitment to nuclear disarmament. The group claims the agreement undermines the country's responsibilities under international treaties. This development has raised concerns among advocates for nuclear disarmament and peace.
